{"tid":1623893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香城：十月圍城，火燒狗車 目標 指南","createTime":"2019-10-05T02:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T12:27:40.000Z","uid":311942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"937973a5192a19259675f3914a2f0bb13eb48d26","tid":1623893,"uid":311942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:10:27.000Z","msg":"故事大綱<br />\n<br />\n破壞中資鋪有無用？有 商界有比壓力政府<br />\n破壞黨鐵有無用？ 有破壞出入閘機 商鋪，黨鐵收入大減<br />\n<br />\n好啦，講到今日一部狗車都無反過肚 無魔法佢過？<br />\n我要大家清晰知道 每一部狗車都係一粒毒瘤<br />\n載黑犬 又捉手足反犬舍 你地諗下 狗車係咪好大禍害？<br />\n<br />\n私家狗車 緊加要搞，破壞公家野，佢地只係少左可以坐嘅交通工具，但私家狗車係佢地個人財產<br />\n所以？會心痛？會驚，會咩？後悔點解搞到埋身囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十月係香港重新嘅開始，梁天琦話過<br />\n黎明前的黑夜是黑暗<br />\n<br />\n而家我地經歷緊！但大家頭腦要再堅定d<br />\n認為啱嘅，繼續做<br />\n<br />\n兄弟手足就算做到幾錯 可以同佢講改善！但四大標準<br />\n不分化 不割席 不篤灰 不譴責<br />\n<br />\n而個星期，我地玩大佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597ff16e809f2cb5e4b75ca1efc2344071f18424","tid":1623893,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:14:37.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"a88641f5f947c3d4351d66d7c15507b25555f4f7","tid":1623893,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:26:52.000Z","msg":"【休息】全民文宣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1623712\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1623712</a>"},{"pid":"7d0f55e26db99770cd98d297fe55fca497592353","tid":1623893,"uid":311942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"597ff16e809f2cb5e4b75ca1efc2344071f18424","tid":1623893,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:14:37.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:35:01.000Z","msg":"幫手再推推！"},{"pid":"d66e1d17e3d81d2a95707825804e8bba3c6b2564","tid":1623893,"uid":311942,